e as readers, take the Bible into our own hands.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 10. Jan 2022) 4aGeneral. 4aLiterary Criticism. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aAmor, Maryann, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBoyer, Alexis Felder, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBurt, Sean, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCwikla, Anna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEmanuel, Sarah, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFein, Sarah E.G., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGraybill, Rhiannon, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGraybill, Rhiannon, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKoosed, Jennifer L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMini, Meredith, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aParks, Sara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSabo, Peter J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSabo, Peter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSeesengood, Robert Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStone, Ken, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStrømmen, Hannah M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTwomey, Jay, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWalsh, Richard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9